cially for systems with\nshort ranged attraction potentials (when $z_1$ and $z_2$ are large). In the Kac\nlimit $z_1,z_2 \\to +0$, both approaches tend to nearly the same results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2004 20:02:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-31"}
