ead to\nthe creation of a material with a controlled concentration of nuclear spins.\nTwo examples of nano-devices for spintronics and quantum computation, based on\nisotopically engineered silicon, are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Mar 2004 09:29:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
